00:31:11,870 --> 00:31:13,913
Yes. I'll drop her off
at the kindergarten.

358
00:31:15,498 --> 00:31:18,084
Gang-hwa, what's gotten into you
yesterday and today?

359
00:31:18,167 --> 00:31:20,128
