I mean, she should've told you
she watched you for five years.

434
00:37:22,698 --> 00:37:25,868
No. How could she tell you that? Goodness.

435
00:37:27,912 --> 00:37:29,080
Have you ever felt like

436
00:37:29,914 --> 00:37:33,417
