481
00:40:33,264 --> 00:40:34,098
Hyeon-jeong.

482
00:40:36,475 --> 00:40:37,601
I was just passing by.

483
00:40:39,395 --> 00:40:41,063
Have some coffee.

484
00:40:42,398 --> 00:40:43,524
-Okay.
-My gosh.

485
00:40:44,108 --> 00:40:45,609
