486
00:40:45,985 --> 00:40:47,111
It's nothing.

487
00:40:51,615 --> 00:40:52,741
Hyeon-jeong!

488
00:40:53,284 --> 00:40:54,952
The weather is warming up now.

489
00:40:56,078 --> 00:40:58,247
Those are some huge anchovies! Oh my.

