What is this place?

493
00:41:19,310 --> 00:41:20,978
A place of business.

494
00:41:22,563 --> 00:41:23,522
I love it.

495
00:41:24,315 --> 00:41:26,692
Having a place I can stop by
in my neighborhood.

496
00:41:27,610 --> 00:41:30,654
